---
import LogoCanvas from "./LogoCanvas.astro";
---

<div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-start">
  <div class="logo-wrapper">
    <div class="logo-bg"></div>
    <LogoCanvas />
  </div>
  <h1 class="text-9xl font-bold text-center title">UYUPUN</h1>
  <p class="text-3xl text-center mb-8 subtitle">xuxyu ... PUNPO PUNPO Technologies, Org.</p>
  <p class="text-left max-w-2xl leading-relaxed"><span class="text-bg">──&ensp;創ることへの純粋な愉しさを原動力に、エンタメとアートの境界で活動中。Web・モバイル・ハードウェアをミックスし、伝統と最新技術を融合したルネサンス的作品を数多く制作。少人数精鋭のキメラ的クリエイティブ集団。あ、もしもし？ぅゅだけど...うん、そうぷんぽぷんぽ(´･ェ･｀)</span></p>
  <p class="text-left max-w-2xl leading-relaxed mt-4"><span class="text-bg">──&ensp;Driven by a pure love of making things, operating at the intersection of entertainment and art. Blending web, mobile, and hardware, we craft renaissance-style works that fuse tradition with cutting-edge technology. A small but fierce chimeric creative collective. Oh, hello? It's uyu... yeah, punpo punpo (´･ェ･｀)</span></p>
</div>

<style>
  .logo-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    width: 700px;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .logo-bg {
    position: absolute;
    width: 400px;
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    background: black;
  }

  .title,
  .subtitle {
    font-family: "Pirata One", cursive;
  }

  .text-bg {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
    padding: 0 0.3em;
    -webkit-box-decoration-break: clone;
    box-decoration-break: clone;
  }
</style>
